{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 02:35:47.464573", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission summary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): leaf_router_0_0\n- Root cause: host_static_blackhole\n\nRationale:\nA static/boot-time blackhole route exists in the kernel FIB of leaf_router_0_0 for 10.0.0.0/24, overriding the connected route and blackholing traffic to/from pc_0_0’s subnet. FRR is healthy and selects the connected route, but the kernel retains the blackhole, causing ping/route-get “Invalid argument” and isolating pc_0_0.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2238, "output_tokens": 126, "total_tokens": 2364, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2176}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
